<font color = "red">
<p>
Video game addiction can be very serious if left unadressed. This website will be your first stop to stopping video game addiction.
</p>

</font>
<h1>
General Information
</h1>
</div>
<font size = 3>
<div align = "left">
<p>
Video game addiction can affect anyone, from young children to adults. Video game addiction has been proven to be very similar to gambling an drug addiction. Video game addiction can be very serious and have long term affects.  
</p>
<p>

Most addictive video games include elements where you communicate with other people such as MMORPG's (Massive Multiplayer Online Role Playing Games).
Some effects of video game addiction include:

<ul>
<li>Anxiety or Depression</li>
<li>Becoming irritated if unable to play</li>
<li>Lying about how long he/she has been playing</li>
<li>Playing in secret</li>
<li>Thinking about video games while doing other activities</li>
<li>Staying up late to play games</li>
<li>Using games to escape from reality</li>
<li>Skipping school/work to play games</li>
<li>Losing intrest in other activities</li>
</ul>
</p>
<h1>
<div align = "center">
Serious Cases
</div>
</h1>
<p>
In some cases, video game addiction can lead to serious injury, mental illness, and sometimes death.
<h3>
<div align = "center">
Girl Dies of Neglect
</div>
</h3>
In South Korea, a three-year-old died girl of neglect when her parents had gone to an internet cafe for 12 hours with their daughter unattended.
when they returned home, she was dead. In their game, the parents were raising a virtual child.
<h3>
<div align = "center">
Teen dies after playing games for 22 days
</div>
</h3>
A 17-year-old boy died after playing games for almost 22 days straight.
He had broken his leg and was staying home from school. He was bored so he played a lot of video games for 22 days just taking snaps. 
He died because he sat still for too long. He had spend more than 2,000 hours playing the game in the past year and a half
<h3>
<div align = "center">
Teen Kills Woman For Money
</div>
</h3>
In Vietnam a thirteen year old boy strangled a woman and buried her in a pile of sand. All of this was for $6.20 he needed to play a video game.
</p>
